{"tid":1277980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊6．26曾聯合演練　一度面向中環金鐘 (18:01)","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:07:13.000Z","uid":167973,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d8b18fad6df21b6646b20f2d057cc3a7110a45","tid":1277980,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"內地《解放軍報》今午（2日）在其官方「軍報記者」微博稱，解放軍駐港部隊曾於6月26日（上周三）進行聯合海空巡邏演練，分別出動陸、海、空三軍部分兵力，在香港附近海空域舉辦聯合海空巡邏演練，以提升部隊緊急出動、臨機處置、聯合行動等作戰能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從照片可見，部分海軍於演練中一度面向中還和金鐘一帶，他們亦有拿長槍瞄向各方位進行演練。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mbycTd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mbycTd.png&h=af2e773b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhrRJZW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhrRJZW.png&h=fb9d3d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，6月26日民陣曾在中環愛丁堡廣場舉行集會，要求特區政府回應撤回《逃犯條例》修訂等訴求；其後大批示威者包圍鄰近的警察總部。<br />\n<br />\nSource:明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190702/s00001/1562061864427/%e8%a7%a3%e6%94%be%e8%bb%8d%e9%a7%90%e6%b8%af%e9%83%a8%e9%9a%8a6-26%e6%9b%be%e8%81%af%e5%90%88%e6%bc%94%e7%b7%b4-%e4%b8%80%e5%ba%a6%e9%9d%a2%e5%90%91%e4%b8%ad%e7%92%b0%e9%87%91%e9%90%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190702%2Fs00001%2F1562061864427%2F%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%2594%25be%25e8%25bb%258d%25e9%25a7%2590%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2583%25a8%25e9%259a%258a6-26%25e6%259b%25be%25e8%2581%25af%25e5%2590%2588%25e6%25bc%2594%25e7%25b7%25b4-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e9%259d%25a2%25e5%2590%2591%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e7%2592%25b0%25e9%2587%2591%25e9%2590%2598&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=fa017e42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190702%2Fs00001%2F1562061864427%2F%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%259